  "title": "Senior Quantity Surveyor / Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Senior Quantity Surveyor / </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Quantity Surveyor</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Report to the Contracts Manager.</li>\n  <li>Prepare tender submissions, manage progress claims, variations orders (VO), and finalise project accounts.</li>\n  <li>Liaise and build good working relationships with consultants, quantity surveyors, architects, and developers.</li>\n  <li>Certify claims for subcontractors and suppliers for progress payments and account finalisation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree or Diploma in Building, Quantity Surveying, Civil, or Structural Engineering.</li>\n  <li>2 to 5 years’ relevant experience with contractors. Candidates with more experience may be considered for Senior QS roles.</li>\n  <li>Experience in Civil Engineering works is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented, proactive, strong problem-solving skills, good team player, and able to meet tight deadlines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Apply now to advance your quantity surveying career!  </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>",
